t, and how to help our friends, and bees!&nbsp;</p>"},{"id":"21035","title":"13-Adventist Identity","imageWithFallback":{"url":"https://s.audioverse.org/english/gallery/seriess/1/50/50/InverseLogo.jpg"},"persons":[{"name":"Justin Kim"},{"name":"Israel Ramos"},{"name":"Jonathan Walter"},{"name":"Callie Williams"}],"duration":2409.5,"recordingDate":"2020-03-28T09:45:00.000Z","audioFiles":[{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/72577/2019/12/21035/20200328-0945-21035-4cbe51e989f52bacb85ae6d24cc0b5ef-96k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/72578/2019/12/21035/20200328-0945-21035-4cbe51e989f52bacb85ae6d24cc0b5ef-48k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/72579/2019/12/21035/20200328-0945-21035-4cbe51e989f52bacb85ae6d24cc0b5ef-16k.mp3"}],"description":"<p>How is the Adventist church rooted in Jesus Christ?</p>"},{"id":"21649","title":"How to Strengthen Your Devotional Life During this COVID-19 Crisis","imageWithFallback":{"url":"https://s.audioverse.org/english/gallery/persons/_/50/50/Shin_David.jpg"},"persons":[{"name":"David Shin"}],"duration":2102.8,"recordingDate":"2020-03-21T13:45:00.000Z","audioFiles":[{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/74920/2020/03/21649/20200321-1345-21649-d8941876af104e0b343eb07b6c53f6f6-96k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/74921/2020/03/21649/20200321-1345-21649-d8941876af104e0b343eb07b6c53f6f6-48k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/74922/2020/03/21649/20200321-1345-21649-d8941876af104e0b343eb07b6c53f6f6-16k.mp3"}],"description":""},{"id":"21648","title":"COVID-19 Update with Dr. Roger Seheult","imageWithFallback":{"url":"https://s.audioverse.org/english/gallery/sponsors/_/50/50/sda_logo.jpg"},"persons":[{"name":"Roger Seheult"}],"duration":3884.5,"recordingDate":"2020-03-21T15:00:00.000Z","audioFiles":[{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/74890/2020/03/21648/20200321-1500-21648-19d9f382b301996913b9640fb31895bf-96k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/74891/2020/03/21648/20200321-1500-21648-19d9f382b301996913b9640fb31895bf-48k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/74892/2020/03/21648/20200321-1500-21648-19d9f382b301996913b9640fb31895bf-16k.mp3"}],"description":"<p>Dr. Seheult, a critical care pulmonologist, shares the latest details on the COVID-19 outbreak and also some practical things Seventh-day Adventists are uniquely positioned to do in the midst of this crisis. Dr. Seheult has also been sharing extensive updates all throughout this outbreak via his <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/MEDCRAMvideos/videos\">MedCram YouTube channel</a>.</p>"},{"id":"21646","title":"How to Thrive in Crisis","imageWithFallback":{"url":"https://s.audioverse.org/english/gallery/persons/_/50/50/Finley_Mark.jpg"},"persons":[{"name":"Mark Finley"}],"duration":3138.9,"recordingDate":"2020-03-21T11:00:00.000Z","audioFiles":[{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/74895/2020/03/21646/20200321-1100-21646-6dd4f73ae1bfd841b718656ffbf7e3be-96k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/74896/2020/03/21646/20200321-1100-21646-6dd4f73ae1bfd841b718656ffbf7e3be-48k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/74897/2020/03/21646/20200321-1100-21646-6dd4f73ae1bfd841b718656ffbf7e3be-16k.mp3"}],"description":"<p>As Coronavirus (COVID-19) continues to spread and fear consumes the world, what can we do? Where is God in all this? The Bible has given us the essentials to survive, even thrive in difficult times. Watch and listen as Pastor Mark Finley presents another message of hope and how you can thrive in life's toughest times.</p>"},{"id":"21644","title":"House Arrest","imageWithFallback":{"url":"https://s.audioverse.org/english/gallery/sponsors/_/50/50/weimar-institute.jpg"},"persons":[{"name":"Allen Lloyd"}],"duration":3241.8,"recordingDate":"2020-03-20T19:00:00.000Z","audioFiles":[{"url